(2230, 369, 'welcome_text', 'Welcome to the North Raleigh campus of The Point Church. ¬†We are excited you are finding out more info about our church. Each one of our campuses has its own distinct flavor but we are one church. Below you‚Äôll find everything you need to plan a visit to the¬†North Raleigh campus.\r\n\r\nBefore you visit we want you to know that you don‚Äôt have to dress up, pretend to be perfect or worry about your past.¬†We just want you to experience Jesus.'),
