(2981, 505, 'what_do_i_do_with_my_kids', 'Kid Point is our children‚Äôs program for birth-5th grade. When you walk through the doors you will see a Kid Point sign ahead and on your right. Just follow the Kid Point Signs to the Check-In Table, and our great Kid Point Volunteers will register your kids so that they can have safe and fun Sunday learning about Jesus.\r\n\r\nStudent Point is our program for Middle School and High School students. Student Point at North Raleigh¬†will begin meeting¬†on Sundays during first service¬†beginning March 20th. For more information, email elise@pointchurch.com'),
