(3209, 537, 'event_content', 'We are excited to launch our newest campus¬†on March 20th with services at 9:15 and 11:00am! We\'ll be kicking off with a new sermon series called, \"The Fix.\" You won\'t want to miss this!\r\n\r\nNo matter your background, where you\'ve been, or what you\'ve done, we\'re here to help you experience Jesus. That\'s why we are starting this new church in North Raleigh.\r\n\r\nFollowing the 11:00am service, we\'re hosting an Easter Egg Hunt at Lake Lynn Park for the kids. You can\'t get info about that here.\r\n\r\nWe hope to see you March 20th!'),
