(5218, 831, 'what_do_i_do_with_my_kids', 'Kid Point is our children‚Äôs program for birth-5th grade. When you walk through the doors you will see a Kid Point sign on your right. Just follow the Kid Point Signs to the Check-In Table, and our great Kid Point Volunteers will register your kids so that they can have safe and fun Sunday learning about Jesus.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Student Point is our program for Middle School and High School students. Student Point for our Apex campus meets at¬†our Cary Campus on Sunday nights from 6:30pm-8:00pm. For more information, email <a href=\"mailto:elise@pointchurch.com\"><span class=\"s2\">elise@pointchurch.com</span></a>.</span></p>'),
