(5252, 832, 'where_do_i_park', 'If it‚Äôs your first time with us just look for the ‚ÄúFirst Time Visitor‚Äù signs¬†on your right¬†as you pull into the parking lot. Those spots are reserved for you. If you have kids, park in the rear of the building by our Family Entrance, just follow the \"Family Entrance\" signs.'),
