(5256, 832, 'what_do_i_do_with_my_kids', 'Kid Point is our children‚Äôs program for birth-5th grade. When you walk through the doors of the Family Entrance in the rear of the building, you will walk into our Kid Point lobby. Follow the hallway to the right and you will quickly see our Family Check-In Station and bathrooms. When you arrive there,¬†our great Kid Point Volunteers will register your kids so they can have a safe and fun Sunday learning about Jesus.\r\n<p class=\"p1\">Student Point is our program for Middle School and High School students. Student Point meets from 11:00am to 12:15pm during the second Sunday morning service. For more information, email <a href=\"mailto:taylors@pointchurch.com\">taylors<span class=\"s2\">@pointchurch.com</span></a>.</p>'),
