(5421, 866, 'welcome_text', '<strong>The Point Church is coming to Fuquay-Varina in August 2017!</strong>\r\n\r\nThe Point Church is a movement of churches across the Triangle with one mission. We are all about pointing people to Jesus. We want to help people take their next steps with him‚Äîno matter where they are in their faith. So there‚Äôs no need to dress up, pretend to be perfect, or worry about your past. We just want you to experience Jesus. We are excited to bring a Point Church to Fuquay-Varina in August 2017 to point people to Jesus!\r\n\r\nFrank White will be leading this new church. He brings a wealth of experience to the team, and is excited to for the opportunity to put a new local church in the Fuquay-Varina community. He says,\r\n<blockquote>Wake County is one of the fastest growing, most desirable places in the nation to live, yet less than 12% of its residents attend an evangelical church. Having served on church staff and as pastor, missionary and denominational leader, and with nearly 10 years of church planting experience in North Carolina, God called us to help address this pressing need.</blockquote>\r\nIf you would like to be a part of this church or would like more info, email frankw@pointchurch.com.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>The Game Plan</strong>\r\n\r\nWe will meet most months for¬†<u>worship, community, and training</u>¬†on the¬†<strong>third <span data-term=\"goog_1615274371\">Saturday</span> monthly!¬†</strong>Some¬†times we will meet for supper afterwards. Check back here each month for updated details.\r\n\r\n<span data-term=\"goog_1615274373\">Jan 21, 2017</span> - <span data-term=\"goog_1615274374\">6:30</span> for Worship &amp; Dessert/Community\r\n\r\n<span data-term=\"goog_1615274375\">Feb 18</span>\r\n\r\n<span data-term=\"goog_1615274376\">March 18</span>\r\n\r\nApril 22\r\n\r\n<span data-term=\"goog_1615274377\">May 20</span>\r\n\r\nMonthly Preview Worship Services: June, July &amp; early August.\r\n\r\nLaunch <span data-term=\"goog_1615274379\">Sunday</span>: <span data-term=\"goog_1615274380\">August 20</span> or¬†<u>27.</u>\r\n\r\nService projects TBD.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;'),
