(6433, 1012, 'this_weeks_sermon_text', 'Each week our dynamic local pastors teach the truths of the Bible in a compelling and meaningful way you can apply to your life. ¬†Click below to hear teaching from our campus.\r\n\r\nBefore you visit we want you to know that you don‚Äôt have to dress up, pretend to be perfect or worry about your past.¬†We just want you to experience Jesus.'),
