(12, 1, '2015-05-07 20:50:16', '2015-05-07 20:50:16', '<h3>Blog</h3>\r\n<a href=\"http://localhost:8000/media/blog/\">Read our blog</a> for meditation inspiration and reading plans.\r\n<h3>Sermons</h3>\r\nVisit our sermon archive at <a href=\"http://www.pointchurchsermons.com\">pointchurchsermons.com</a>.\r\n<h3>App</h3>\r\nDownload our <a href=\"https://a3a.me/point\">Point Church App</a>.\r\n<h3>Videos</h3>\r\nAll of our videos are hosted on <a href=\"https://vimeo.com/churchpoint\">our Vimeo profile</a>.\r\n<h3>Music</h3>\r\nTo listen to the songs we sing on Sundays check out our <a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/user/pointworship\">Spotify Playlist</a>.\r\n<h3>Curriculum</h3>\r\nTo download the latest curriculum, <a href=\"http://www.pointchurch.com/media/curriculum/\">visit our curriculum page</a>.\r\n<h3>Annual Report</h3>\r\nTo view this past year\'s Annual Report, <a href=\"http://localhost:8000/media/annual-report/\">click here</a>.\r\n<h3>Facilities Request</h3>\r\nWould you like¬†to use our space? <a href=\"https://point.ccbchurch.com/w_form_response.php?form_id=86\">Fill out this online form</a>.', 'Media', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'media', '', '', '2017-02-22 10:31:41', '2017-02-22 15:31:41', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/point-church/?page_id=12', 5, 'page', '', 0),
(14, 1, '2015-05-07 20:50:23', '2015-05-07 20:50:23', '<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">ONLINE GIVING</h2>\r\nOnline giving is a safe and easy way to give back to God and support the ministries of The Point Church. This system enables you to support the church by making a one-time contribution or establishing a recurring contribution. Recurring giving is a great way to make sure you are faithful to God with your giving commitments and the church is financially stable. Additionally, keeping your information and contribution secure is a top priority of The Point Church.\r\n<div class=\"buttons\"><a class=\"button\" href=\"https://pushpay.com/pay/pointchurch\">Give Online</a></div>\r\nTwo Simple Steps:\r\n<ol class=\"ol1\">\r\n	<li class=\"li1\">Provide contact and credit card or bank draft information (bank drafts have lower processing fees).</li>\r\n	<li class=\"li1\">Indicate the amount, frequency (one-time or recurring) and designation for your gift.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">GENEROSITY PATHWAY</h2>\r\nGenerosity is a critical part of our growth as a follower of Jesus. However, it doesn\'t always come naturally. We believe that as we become more generous, we become more like Jesus. So we have developed our Generosity Pathway to help you take next steps in generosity. Use this tool to find where you are in generosity and discern your next step.Click here to listen to a message about growing in generosity.\r\n<div class=\"buttons\"><a class=\"button\" href=\"http://www.pointchurchsermons.com/?enmse=1&amp;enmse_sid=22&amp;enmse_mid=95\">Generosity Message</a></div>\r\n<a href=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Generosity-Pathway-simple.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-480\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-480 aligncenter\" src=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Generosity-Pathway-simple.jpg\" alt=\"Generosity-Pathway-simple\" width=\"600\" height=\"603\" /></a>', 'Give', 