(39, 1, '2015-08-09 21:36:14', '2015-08-09 21:36:14', '<h3 class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Sunday Morning:¬†</span></h3>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Our South Raleigh Church Campus is only a few miles from NC STATE!¬†</span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li class=\"p3\"><span class=\"s1\"><strong>Location:¬†</strong><a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/place/The+Point+Church/@35.770669,-78.6963114,13z/data=!4m13!1m7!3m6!1s0x89acf534f5ffd7e9:0xe75ea031edd103a9!2s3700+Lake+Wheeler+Rd,+Raleigh,+NC+27603!3b1!8m2!3d35.7306339!4d-78.6832778!3m4!1s0x89acf59906010165:0x4f0223093abb34c4!8m2!3d35.7306339!4d-78.6832778\" target=\"_blank\">3700 Lake Wheeler Rd, Raleigh</a></span></li>\r\n	<li class=\"p3\"><span class=\"s1\"><strong>Service Times:</strong>¬†9:15am &amp; 11:00am</span></li>\r\n	<li class=\"p3\"><span class=\"s1\"><strong>Shuttle:</strong> 10:15 at¬†<a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/place/Talley+Student+Union/@35.7838484,-78.6731279,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m2!3m1!1s0x89acf591a97d2d79:0x38989377c96adef0\" target=\"_blank\">Talley Student Center</a> @ NC State</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3><strong>Point Church Shuttle</strong></h3>\r\n<a href=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Point-Church-Shuttle-Magnet.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-497\"><img class=\"alignright wp-image-497 \" src=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Point-Church-Shuttle-Magnet-300x235.jpg\" alt=\"Point Shuttle\" width=\"141\" height=\"110\" /></a>Need a ride to church? No problem. We have a shuttle that picks up at¬†the front of <a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/place/Talley+Student+Union/@35.7838484,-78.6731279,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m2!3m1!1s0x89acf591a97d2d79:0x38989377c96adef0\" target=\"_blank\">Talley Student Center</a> every <strong>Sunday at 10:15am</strong> during the school year. For more information email Corey Gravil¬†at <a href=\"mailto:coreyg@pointchurch.com\">coreyg@pointchurch.com</a>.\r\n<h3><strong>Life Group</strong></h3>\r\n<a href=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Life-Groups.png\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-495\"><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-495 size-thumbnail\" src=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Life-Groups-150x150.png\" alt=\"Life Groups\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>On <strong>Wednesday nights at 7pm</strong> our college students meet at the <strong>Student Center (The Den)</strong> located at <a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/place/2526+Hillsborough+St+%23205,+Raleigh,+NC+27607/@35.7883425,-78.6714205,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m2!3m1!1s0x89acf59264373f7f:0x5d7add9a66e94b3\">2526 Hillsborough St, Suite 205, Raleigh</a>. At Life Group we build community, hear dynamic teaching, and break out in smaller groups for discussion. It is the first step for college students to grow in their¬†faith and build relationships at The Point!\r\n<h3><strong>Mission/Vision</strong></h3>\r\nOur mission is to point college students to Jesus. Our vision is to have a local campus of The Point Church impacting every college in the Triangle.\r\n<h3><strong>Strategy</strong></h3>\r\nWe want to make it hard not to go to church while you are at college. We do this by creating an exciting environment for students to go to church that is close and casual. We are on campus weekly making sure students know about our church family. Finally, we have an intentional plan to help college students at our church take next steps to become more like Jesus.\r\n<h3><strong>Upcoming Events</strong></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>8/14 at¬†11:00am - <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">Welcome Sunday</span></strong>: Come to our Sunday service and we will serve college students a free catered lunch after church!</li>\r\n	<li><strong>8/14 at 7:30pm - <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">Bonfire &amp; S\'mores</span></strong>: At our South Raleigh Campus (<a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/place/The+Point+Church/@35.770669,-78.6963114,13z/data=!4m13!1m7!3m6!1s0x89acf534f5ffd7e9:0xe75ea031edd103a9!2s3700+Lake+Wheeler+Rd,+Raleigh,+NC+27603!3b1!8m2!3d35.7306339!4d-78.6832778!3m4!1s0x89acf59906010165:0x4f0223093abb34c4!8m2!3d35.7306339!4d-78.6832778\" target=\"_blank\">3700 Lake Wheeler Rd, Raleigh</a>)</li>\r\n	<li><strong>8/17 at 7:00pm - <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">First College Life Group</span></strong>:¬†Meet at the Den (<a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/place/2526+Hillsborough+St+%23205,+Raleigh,+NC+27607/@35.7883425,-78.6714205,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m2!3m1!1s0x89acf59264373f7f:0x5d7add9a66e94b3\">2526 Hillsborough St, Suite 205</a>) and then we will have a Video Scavenger Hunt!</li>\r\n	<li><strong>8/21 at 9:15 &amp; 11:00am¬†- <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">College Football Sunday</span></strong>: Featuring Jack Tocho, Nick Lacy, and Jalan McClendon</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Wednesdays¬†at 7:00pm - <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">College Life Group</span></strong>: At the Den (<a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/place/2526+Hillsborough+St+%23205,+Raleigh,+NC+27607/@35.7883425,-78.6714205,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m2!3m1!1s0x89acf59264373f7f:0x5d7add9a66e94b3\">2526 Hillsborough St, Suite 205</a>)</li>\r\n</ul>', 'College Point', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'college-point', '', '', '2016-08-17 12:08:50', '2016-08-17 17:08:50', '', 10, 'http://localhost:8888/point-church/?page_id=39', 3, 'page', '', 0),
