(624, 4, '2016-05-26 09:40:05', '2016-05-26 14:40:05', '<h3 class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>Description</b></span></h3>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">The Senior Point Ministry is our ministry to Senior Citizens at The Point Church.¬† The mission of our Senior Point ministry is to intentionally point seniors in the Triangle to Jesus through Lifegroups, Services, Socials, and Monthly Gatherings. ¬†</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"p3\"><span class=\"s2\"><b>Monthly Gathering</b></span></h3>\r\n<p class=\"p3\"><span class=\"s2\">\"Silver Bells\" - Third Tuesday of Each Month from 11:30-1:30 at the South Raleigh Campus -¬†</span><span class=\"s1\">3700 Lake Wheeler Rd, Raleigh, NC 27603. Bring a covered dish.¬† Come enjoy great teaching, food, and community!¬†</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"p3\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>Life Groups</b></span></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li class=\"p3\"><span class=\"s1\"><strong>Hardee Life Group</strong> on <strong><span style=\"color: #00a0c6;\">Sunday Mornings at 9:15am</span></strong> - S. Raleigh Campus (<a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/place/The+Point+Church/@35.7306382,-78.6854718,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m5!3m4!1s0x89acf59906010165:0x4f0223093abb34c4!8m2!3d35.7306339!4d-78.6832778\" target=\"_blank\">3700 Lake Wheeler Rd</a>). Lead by Jim Hardee (<a href=\"mailto:hardeejim@gmail.com\">hardeejim@gmail.com</a>). All adults welcome!</span></li>\r\n	<li class=\"p3\"><span class=\"s1\"><strong>Hall Life Group</strong> on <strong><span style=\"color: #00a0c6;\">Sunday Mornings at 9:15am</span></strong> - S. Raleigh Campus (<a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/place/The+Point+Church/@35.7306382,-78.6854718,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m5!3m4!1s0x89acf59906010165:0x4f0223093abb34c4!8m2!3d35.7306339!4d-78.6832778\" target=\"_blank\">3700 Lake Wheeler Rd</a>). Lead by Terry Hall¬†(<a href=\"mailto:thall001@bellsouth.net\">thall001@bellsouth.net</a>). All adults welcome!</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"p3\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"s1\">For more information email <a href=\"mailto:info@pointchurch.com\"><span class=\"s3\">info@pointchurch.com</span></a> with any questions or more details.</span></p>', '', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'senior-point', '', '', '2016-05-27 08:54:11', '2016-05-27 13:54:11', '', 10, 'http://localhost:8000/?page_id=624', 5, 'page', '', 0),
