(627, 4, '2016-05-26 10:08:29', '2016-05-26 15:08:29', '<h3 class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>Description</b></span></h3>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">The Young Pros ministry at The Point Church is a place for young adults in their 20‚Äôs to mid-30‚Äôs to find specific teaching for their life stage, meet other young pros in the Triangle, and get connected to the life of the church.¬† The mission of our Young Pros ministry is to point Young Pros in the Triangle to Jesus through our network of small groups, opportunities to serve, socials, and quarterly ministry nights.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"p3\">Life Group Network</h3>\r\n<strong>Sunday¬†Night Raleigh Life Group (7pm-9pm)</strong>\r\nLocation:¬†<a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/place/1013+Early+Rise+St,+Raleigh,+NC+27610/@35.7328483,-78.6231882,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m5!3m4!1s0x89ac5fd026de47c3:0x406669b38971a190!8m2!3d35.7328483!4d-78.6209942\">1013 Early Rise St, Raleigh 27610</a>\r\nLeader: Justin Patton (justinp@pointchurch.com)\r\n\r\n<strong><span class=\"aBn\" tabindex=\"0\" data-term=\"goog_328436652\"><span class=\"aQJ\">Monday</span></span> Night Life Group (<span class=\"aBn\" tabindex=\"0\" data-term=\"goog_328436653\"><span class=\"aQJ\">7pm-9pm</span></span>)</strong>\r\nLocation: <a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/place/4511+Edwards+Mill+Rd+e,+Raleigh,+NC+27612/@35.8384913,-78.6900207,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m5!3m4!1s0x89acf6425717967b:0x5a84ed10918354b9!8m2!3d35.838487!4d-78.687832\" target=\"_blank\">4511 Edwards Mill Rd. Apt E Raleigh, NC 27612</a>\r\nLeader: Jake Kausler (<a href=\"mailto:jakekausler@yahoo.com\" target=\"_blank\">jakekausler@yahoo.com</a>)\r\n\r\n<strong>Tuesday Night Cary Life Group (7pm-9pm)</strong>\r\nLocation:¬†<a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/place/315+E+Cornwall+Rd,+Cary,+NC+27511/@35.7751853,-78.7775027,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m5!3m4!1s0x89acf30bfa95d7fd:0x87b78068bae6e416!8m2!3d35.775181!4d-78.775314\" target=\"_blank\">315 East Cornwall Road, Cary, NC 27511</a>\r\nLeader: John Gilbert (<a href=\"mailto:jpatt8811@gmail.com\" target=\"_blank\">j</a><a href=\"mailto:ohng@pointchurch.com\" target=\"_blank\">ohng@pointchurch.com</a>)\r\n<h3 class=\"p3\">Connect With Us</h3>\r\n<p class=\"p3\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span class=\"s1\">For more information email justinp@pointchurch.com¬†or check out our <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/214239295636071/?hc_ref=SEARCH\" target=\"_blank\">facebook page</a>.</span></p>', '', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'pointyoungpros', '', '', '2017-04-07 08:28:44', '2017-04-07 13:28:44', '', 10, 'http://localhost:8000/?page_id=627', 4, 'page', '', 0),
