(632, 4, '2016-05-27 08:51:28', '2016-05-27 13:51:28', '<h3>Students</h3>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">The Point Church Student Ministry has 5 steps to help your student grow spiritually, get plugged in to community and build on their relationship with Christ. The Point Church Next Steps path is Worship-Connect-Serve-Grow-Lead, this provides clear steps to grow more like Jesus.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h4 class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>Experience | Worship</b></span></h4>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">We challenge each student to attend service with their parents as a family. We believe that it is so beneficial to be a part of the church service at each students campus.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h4 class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>Connect | Life Groups</b></span></h4>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Our Student Life Groups are called Student Point. We use Orange Curriculum for our teaching at all Student Point gatherings. This curriculum is organized around 3-8 week series that hit on key topics that tie to our Family Discipleship Plan. Each Student Point gathering will include theme based activities, video teaching, and small group discussion time.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Cary and Apex meet Sunday nights at the Cary Campus from 6:30-8:00pm.</span></li>\r\n	<li class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">North Raleigh meets on Sunday mornings during first service. Then as a family you can attend 2nd service.</span></li>\r\n	<li class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">South Raleigh meets on Wednesday nights at the South Raleigh Campus from 6:30-8:00pm.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>Serve | Serve Others</b></span></h4>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">All of our students come together to serve at our Cary Food Pantry on the third Saturday of each month. We scheduling regular all campus fellowship opportunities for our entire Student Ministry to be together as one Student Ministry in multiple locations for serving and for fun activities.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h4 class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>Grow | Core Groups</b></span></h4>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">We have Core Groups of small, single gender groups of students who read through scripture together throughout the week. They are a way to grow deeper individually and in community leading to rapid spiritual growth.¬† Email <a href=\"mailto:elise@pointchurch.com\"><span class=\"s2\">elise@pointchurch.com</span></a> to get plugged into a Core Group!</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h4 class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>Lead | Influence</b></span></h4>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Jesus came to lead people to God. WE are called to lead others to follow Him as we invest in the lives of others, through becoming a leader at our church.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Check us out on Social Media:</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/pointchurchstudents/\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-571 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/button-instagram.png\" alt=\"button-instagram\" width=\"41\" height=\"41\" /></a>¬† ¬†<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pointchurchstudents/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-570\"><img class=\"wp-image-570 size-full alignnone\" src=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/button-facebook.png\" alt=\"button-facebook\" width=\"41\" height=\"41\" /></a>¬† ¬†<a href=\"http://www.pointchurchstudents.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-568\"><img class=\"wp-image-568 size-full alignnone\" src=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/button-blog.png\" alt=\"button-blog\" width=\"41\" height=\"41\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>Question? </b>Contact Elise Drennan at <b><a href=\"mailto:elise@pointchurch.com\" target=\"_blank\">elise@pointchurch.com</a></b></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Contact Info</h3>\r\nTo get more info about our upcoming events or meet with one of our leaders, just contact <a href=\"mailto:info@pointchurch.com\">info@pointchurch.com</a> or call 919-467-9159.', '', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'studentpoint', '', '', '2016-05-27 08:53:02', '2016-05-27 13:53:02', '', 10, 'http://localhost:8000/?page_id=632', 2, 'page', '', 0),
