(668, 4, '2016-07-01 09:12:10', '2016-07-01 14:12:10', '<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">We invite you to serve with us in our community <strong>July 18th through 23rd</strong>. We will be serving our community and our world that week by passing out flyers for our food pantries, packing care packages to go to overseas, having a special event at the food pantries for the community, and more! Spots at each project are limited, so be sure to click the link below to sign up:</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"s1\"><a href=\"https://point.ccbchurch.com/form_response.php?id=74\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-671\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-671 size-medium\" src=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/SignUpHere-button-300x79.jpg\" alt=\"SignUpHere-button\" width=\"300\" height=\"79\" /></a>¬†</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Care Center Projects:</span></h3>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\"><strong>Flyer Projects</strong>- Meet at the Apex, Cary, or S. Raleigh campus and distribute flyers about the Big Day in nearby neighborhoods.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\"><strong>Big Day Cooking Teams</strong>- Do you love to cook for big groups? Do you enjoy grilling? If so, the cooking team is a great fit for you! Since we will have extra food at the Big Day, we will need extra hands on deck to cook for our guests.¬† Come at 9am at the Care Pantry at the Apex, Cary or South Raleigh Campus.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\"><strong>The Big Day</strong>- The Big Day is a special celebration day for our Care Pantry guests that will include inflatables, games, and extra food! The Big Day will take place at all three of our Care Pantry locations- Cary, Apex, and South Raleigh.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\"><strong>Sorting Care Pantry Items-</strong> Each week we get lots of items from the NC Food Bank that need to be sorted and stocked at the Apex Campus. Come help us on a Monday morning at the Apex Campus as we sort the food that will be distributed to our guests!</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\"><strong>Grocery Bag Packing</strong>- Each week we provide our guests with two bags of groceries. In order for things to run efficiently, we have to back the bags in advance. Come help us with this on Thursday night at one of our Care Pantry locations in Apex, Cary or South Raleigh!</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\"><strong>Care Pantry Sorting Night</strong>- We will tidy up the Care Pantry room at the Cary Campus! Activities will include sorting and organizing both clothing and food items. Come join us for this fun evening of serving!</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">¬†</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Global Missions Projects‚Äî7pm @ the Cary Campus</span></h3>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\"><strong>Dominican Republic Encouragement Project</strong>- The staff and students at our partner ministry in the Dominican Republic can be greatly blessed through letters of encouragement! Come join us as we make fun cards and letters to send to them.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\"><strong>India Care Bags</strong>- We will be packing bags to go to India. Please bring donations of soap, toothbrushes, toothpaste, and shampoo to pack the bags with!</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\"><strong>Canaan Project Encouragements</strong>- We will be compiling videos of encouragement for a family in our church that is serving in the Middle East. Come help us love and empower this family as they carry to gospel to the unreached!</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">¬†</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Camp Kid Point Projects:</span></h3>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\"><strong>Camp Kid Point Decorating Team</strong>- The night before Camp Kid Point, help us decorate the area and make it look awesome for camp!</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\"><strong>Camp Kid Point</strong>- This awesome one day camp is a great opportunity to invest in the lives of children in our church as well as in our community. Come see what happens in Kid Point every Sunday!</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">¬†</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Other Projects:</span></h3>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\"><strong>Brookridge Bingo and Care Project</strong>- Playing Bingo and having fun with the residents of the Brookridge Assisted Living Home. Meet at ¬†from 6:30‚Äî8pm 312 Lynch St, Apex, NC 27502 for this project!</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\"><strong>Thrift 2 Gift</strong>- Come help us sort and pack donations at Thrift 2 Gift in Apex!</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\"><strong>North Raleigh Ministries</strong>- We will partner with this awesome thrift store and crisis center in North Raleigh for two nights of fun! Activities will include sorting donations, reshelving food items, and helping out as needed. Meet at 9650 Strickland Rd #161, Raleigh, NC 27615 ¬†for this project!</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"p1\">Projects By Date:</h3>\r\n<table style=\"width: 100%; border: 1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px; border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:10px;\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr style=\"background-color:#CCCCCC;\">\r\n<td><strong>Date</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>Project</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>Life Group</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>Location</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>7/18</td>\r\n<td>Apex Flyer Project-6:30pm</td>\r\n<td>Life Group en Espa√±ol</td>\r\n<td>Apex Campus</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>7/18</td>\r\n<td>Food Pantry Sorting- 6:30pm</td>\r\n<td>Raleigh Young Marrieds</td>\r\n<td>Apex Campus</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>7/18</td>\r\n<td>North Raleigh Ministries- 6:30pm</td>\r\n<td>Six Forks Rd. LG, Leesville Rd LG</td>\r\n<td>9650 Strickland Rd #161, Raleigh, NC 27615</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>7/18</td>\r\n<td>Cary Pantry Sorting Project- 6:30pm</td>\r\n<td>Ladies Life Group</td>\r\n<td>Cary Campus</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>7/19</td>\r\n<td>Cary Flyer Project- 6:30pm</td>\r\n<td>Hwy 64</td>\r\n<td>Cary Campus</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>7/19</td>\r\n<td>S. Raleigh Flyer Project- 6:30pm</td>\r\n<td>College Point</td>\r\n<td>South Raleigh Campus</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>7/19</td>\r\n<td>Global Missions Care Bags- 7pm</td>\r\n<td>Young Pros Ministry</td>\r\n<td>Cary Campus</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>7/20</td>\r\n<td>Brookridge Bingo &amp; Care Project 6:30-8pm</td>\r\n<td>Davis Drive Life Group</td>\r\n<td>312 Lynch St, Apex, NC 27502</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>7/20</td>\r\n<td>North Raleigh Ministries- 6:30pm</td>\r\n<td>Creedmoor Rd. LG, Glenwood Ave. LG</td>\r\n<td>9650 Strickland Rd #161, Raleigh, NC 27615</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>7/20</td>\r\n<td>Thrift 2 Gift Project- 6:30pm</td>\r\n<td>Holly Springs Young Pros</td>\r\n<td>Apex Campus</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>7/21</td>\r\n<td>Care Pantry Grocery Packing- Apex, 7pm</td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n<td>Apex Campus</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>7/21</td>\r\n<td>Care Pantry Grocery Packing- S. Raleigh, 7pm</td>\r\n<td>Raleigh Young Marrieds</td>\r\n<td>S. Raleigh Campus</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>7/21</td>\r\n<td>Care Pantry Grocery Packing-Cary, 7pm</td>\r\n<td>Possibly Beaver Creek LG</td>\r\n<td>Cary Campus</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>7/22</td>\r\n<td>Camp Kid Point Decorating Project- 6:30pm</td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n<td>S. Raleigh Campus</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>7/23</td>\r\n<td>Camp Kid Point- 8am-5pm</td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n<td>S. Raleigh Campus</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>7/23</td>\r\n<td>Big Day Cooking Team- Apex, 9am</td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n<td>Apex Campus</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>7/23</td>\r\n<td>Big Day Cooking Team- Cary, 9am</td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n<td>Cary Campus</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>7/23</td>\r\n<td>Big Day Cooking Team- S. Raleigh, 9am</td>\r\n<td></td>\r\