(699, 4, '2016-08-05 08:47:14', '2016-08-05 13:47:14', '<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Hey Church Family,</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">We hope that your faith was increased this past Sunday in the Bible as the Authoritative Word of God. We also understand that you probably still have plenty of questions, and you should. As promised, here\'s an assortment of resources for you to dive into. Save this email, because it will take you a long time to peruse all of the contents linked in this email.¬†</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"p1\">Links</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li class=\"p3\"><span class=\"s2\"><a href=\"http://www.theologynetwork.org/christian-beliefs/the-bible/getting-stuck-in/the-factual-reliability-of-the-old-testament.htm\" target=\"_blank\">The Factual Reliability of the Old Testament - Kenneth Kitchen</a></span></li>\r\n	<li class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\"><a href=\"http://static1.1.sqspcdn.com/static/f/38692/303409/1266585317907/The+New+Testament+Documents+Are+They+Reliable.pdf?token=IwiyVirnT0jWSrZ8cIId839oSoE%3D\" target=\"_blank\">The New Testament Documents: Are They Reliable? - F.F. Bruce</a></span></li>\r\n	<li class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\"><a href=\"http://patternsofevidence.com/blog/2016/04/15/new-evidence-suggests-bible-written-earlier-than-many-scholars-believed/\" target=\"_blank\">New Evidence Suggests Bible Written Earlier Than Many Scholars Believed</a>¬†</span></li>\r\n	<li class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\"><a href=\"https://answersingenesis.org/archaeology/does-archaeology-support-the-bible/\" target=\"_blank\">Does Archaeology Spell the Bible? - Answers in Genesis</a></span></li>\r\n	<li class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\"><a href=\"http://coldcasechristianity.com/category/writings/bible/\" target=\"_blank\">Blog Posts on Biblical Reliability by J. Warner Wallace</a></span></li>\r\n	<li class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\"><a href=\"http://www.faithefc.org/blomberg\" target=\"_blank\">Lectures by Craig Blomberg on \'How we got our Bible\' and \'Can we still believe the Bible?\'</a></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s4\"><b>Book Recommendations</b></span></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Evidence That Demands a Verdict - Josh McDowell</span></li>\r\n	<li class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Cold-Case Christianity - J. Warner Wallace</span></li>\r\n	<li class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Can We Still Believe the Bible? - Craig Blomberg</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">We also mentioned that we would be sending out a link of a song for those of you with children, to help them memorize the books of the Bible. If you\'re an adult and you don\'t have children, there\'s a good chance the song could get stuck in your head and help you memorize them as well.¬†</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"p1\">Books of the Bible Songs</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li class=\"p3\"><span class=\"s2\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=i7ZtWRSCH7E\" target=\"_blank\">Old Testament Song</a></span></li>\r\n	<li class=\"p3\"><span class=\"s2\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ppxke-s6sCA\" target=\"_blank\">New Testament Song</a></span></li>\r\n</ul>', 'doesthebibletellmeso', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'doesthebibletellmeso', '', '', '2016-08-05 08:48:11', '2016-08-05 13:48:11', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8000/?page_id=699', 0, 'page', '', 0),
