(742, 4, '2016-09-07 10:10:28', '2016-09-07 15:10:28', '<a href=\"http://localhost:8000/give\">GIVE ONLINE</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://point.ccbchurch.com/form_response.php?id=97\" target=\"_blank\">COMMITMENT CARD</a>\r\n<h3>What is ‚ÄúWhat If?‚Äù</h3>\r\nTwo years ago The Point Church family asked a ‚ÄúWhat if?‚Äù question. ‚ÄúWhat if we go ALL IN to point more people to Jesus than ever before?‚Äù We believed in faith that God might double the number of people we reach in Wake County. That‚Äôs exactly what happened! We‚Äôve gone from averaging 443 people in weekly attendance to 900. We‚Äôve also baptized over 150 people since the start of All In!\r\n\r\nWe are entering a new season of faith and expectancy called, ‚ÄúWhat If?‚Äù. What if God wants to do something miraculous in and through us again over the next two years?\r\n\r\nThe leadership of The Point Church is confident that He does. The ‚ÄúWhat If?‚Äùquestion this time is this: What if we could go from 6 to 10 healthy campuses over the next 2 years?\r\n<h3>Next Steps</h3>\r\nWe are asking you to go on a ‚ÄúWhat If?‚Äù journey with God and your family. What if you believed the promises of God were true in your life? We are asking you to live as if they are and take the biggest step of generosity you‚Äôve ever taken to accomplish all that God has for us.\r\n\r\nThere are 3 steps that we‚Äôre asking you to take:\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"color: #00a0c6;\"><strong>Pray.</strong></span> Pray that God would show us what is possible if we believe His promises are true. Pray that He would do abundantly more than we ask or imagine to point people to Jesus</li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"color: #00a0c6;\"><strong>Commit.</strong></span> Help us reach our goal of 100 percent participation in this life-changing experience. Stand side by side with your church family. Commit to do whatever God asks and put your ‚Äúyes‚Äù on the table.</li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"color: #00a0c6;\"><strong>Give.</strong></span> Ask God to show you during this season what a sacrificial gift looks like, and take whatever bold steps are required to see it through.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n<h3>Resources</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/What-If-Booklet-small-1.pdf\">What If Guide Book</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"http://localhost:8000/give/\">Give Online</a></li>\r\n</ul>', 'What If', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'what-if', '', '', '2017-03-17 11:02:46', '2017-03-17 16:02:46', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8000/?page_id=742', 0, 'page', '', 0),
