(863, 3, '2016-12-30 14:41:09', '2016-12-30 19:41:09', '&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/The-Power-of-Same-FB-Cover.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-864\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-864\" src=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/The-Power-of-Same-FB-Cover.jpg\" alt=\"The Power of Same-FB Cover\" width=\"851\" height=\"315\" /></a>\r\n\r\nHappy New Year!\r\n\r\nThe word SAME often has a negative connotation because we think of doing the same things as being boring and mundane. However, what if doing the same things over were actually the key to a rich and fulfilling life? What if correctly doing the same things over could help you gain the power to become the person you desire to be? Join us <span class=\"aBn\" tabindex=\"0\" data-term=\"goog_1425431813\"><span class=\"aQJ\">this SUNDAY</span></span> as we start our new series and discover THE POWER OF SAME.\r\n\r\nWe know that‚Äôs <span class=\"aBn\" tabindex=\"0\" data-term=\"goog_1425431814\"><span class=\"aQJ\">January 1</span></span>, and some of you may still be traveling for the holidays, but we believe this series can be life changing. So, here are a few things we invite you to do:\r\n\r\n1. Listen to the first message <a href=\"http://pointchurchsermons.com/\" target=\"_blank\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?hl=en&amp;q=http://pointchurchsermons.com&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1483212189017000&amp;usg=AFQjCNEcpc52Ofoqh4ERNN670ZP8QURMEA\">here </a>or on The Point Church app following <span class=\"aBn\" tabindex=\"0\" data-term=\"goog_1425431815\"><span class=\"aQJ\">this Sunday</span></span> if you are going to be out of town.\r\n\r\n2. Read the book of Mark with us! ¬†Study one chapter of Mark each weekday starting <span class=\"aBn\" tabindex=\"0\" data-term=\"goog_1425431816\"><span class=\"aQJ\">January 2nd</span></span>. ¬†However, don\'t just read it, but meditate on it. <a href=\"https://pointchurch.box.com/shared/static/4cvare3nz5emqlscvcirjsug3ms9j66l.jpg\">Check out this meditation tool called, S.O.A.P.</a>¬†and this S.O.A.P <a href=\"https://pointchurch.box.com/shared/static/5lunho7ooxedt5egr2evrurdbgrwbgjj.jpg\">example</a>.\r\n\r\n3. Check out <a href=\"http://localhost:8000/blog/\">this blog</a>¬†for Mark meditations each weekday through <span class=\"aBn\" tabindex=\"0\" data-term=\"goog_1425431817\"><span class=\"aQJ\">January 20</span></span>.\r\n\r\n4. Download <a href=\"https://a3a.me/point\" target=\"_blank\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?hl=en&amp;q=https://a3a.me/point&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1483212189017000&amp;usg=AFQjCNFrisIdVJAhhOnQujsNCTO3hS314Q\">The Point Church App</a> and turn on the push notifications to get a daily reminder.\r\n\r\nWe want 2017 to be your best year with God. We believe it can be through the power of same.', 'The Power of Same', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'the-power-of-same', '', '', '2017-01-04 01:33:47', '2017-01-04 06:33:47', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8000/?p=863', 0, 'post', '', 0),
