(871, 4, '2017-01-01 20:59:08', '2017-01-02 01:59:08', '<strong>S for Scripture: Mark 1:35</strong>\r\n\r\n<b>‚Äú¬†</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Very early in the morning, while it was still dark, Jesus got up, left the house and went off to a solitary place, where he prayed.‚Äù</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>O for Observation:</strong>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Jesus got up early to spend time with God . . . not just early, he got up </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">very</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> early, while it was </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">still dark</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. ¬†Also, Jesus was very intentional to go to a </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">solitary place</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> where he could be alone with God. ¬†In fact, it was so solitary that it says in the next two verses that his disciples formed a mini search party to find him.</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>A for Application:</strong>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">I cannot hope to be like Jesus without doing the things that he did. ¬†I cannot hope to have the relationship that Jesus had with God without spending the time with God that Jesus did! ¬†I must develop and fight for a routine of getting up early to spend time with God every day so that I can develop into the man of God that he created me to be!</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>P for Prayer:</strong>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Father, please help me to spend more time with you every day in 2017 than ever before so that I can fall more in love with you and look more like Jesus than ever before in 2017. ¬†In Jesus‚Äô name. ¬†Amen. ¬†</span>', 'S.O.A.P. | Mark 1', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 's-o-a-p-mark-1', '', '', '2017-01-01 20:59:08', '2017-01-02 01:59:08', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8000/?p=871', 0, 'post', '', 0),
