(1030, 4, '2017-03-09 16:55:50', '2017-03-09 21:55:50', 'Through the <b>Care Fund</b> we provide <i>financial assistance</i> for those who need it in emergencies. We want to be there for you if you are in a time of need and provide longer term support.\r\n\r\nIf you are interested in submitting a request for assistance please download this <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1W4DuXQ866-9uqmefRhvuG5t2Dp5RQA1AyjJfQ1f_czY/edit\">Request For Assistance Form</a>. You can fill it out, scan it, and email it to <a href=\"mailto:hannahl@pointchurch.com\">hannahl@pointchurch.com</a> or bring it by our offices Tuesday-Friday at normal business hours at 1503 Walnut St. Cary, NC 27511. Please allow 10 days for your application to be processed.', 'Care Fund', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '70-autosave-v1', '', '', '2017-03-09 16:55:50', '2017-03-09 21:55:50', '', 70, 'http://localhost:8000/2017/03/09/70-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1031, 4, '2017-03-12 09:40:03', '2017-03-12 14:40:03', '<h2>S for Scripture:</h2>\r\n\"Do not be anxious about anything, but in every situation, by prayer and petition, with thanksgiving, present your requests to God. And the peace of God, which transcends all understanding, will guard your hearts and your minds in Christ Jesus.‚Äù ‚Äî Philippians 4:6-7\r\n<h2>O for Observation:</h2>\r\nPaul is explaining to children of God how to think and behave like children of God. Something I love about this is that it is not just good advice on how to live healthily or to be good, but rather it‚Äôs a picture of how to live as a person who is loved by the God of the universe. \r\nI have plenty examples in my life of seasons where anxiety was not just present, but felt overwhelming. And I look back at those times and realize I was anxious in light of how I related to God in that situation. I would not remember that he is bigger and more powerful than what life was throwing at me. I would forget that His plans for my life were infinitely more fulfilling and good for me than what I thought I wanted. Life will be difficult so who do I really believe God is during those times, and who do I really believe I am as a child of God in those times. \r\n<h2>A for Application:</h2>\r\nAnxiety and worry should be a red flag for me. Those emotions should trigger a response of asking how can I trust Him more in this situation. \r\n<h2>P for Prayer:</h2>\r\nFather teach me to live in what it means to be a child of yours. I pray that I would quickly recognize times in my life where I drift away from that identity. Thank you for your peace.', 'Promise #15 - Peace', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'promise-15-peace', '', '', '2017-03-12 09:40:03', '2017-03-12 14:40:03', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8000/?p=1031', 0, 'post', '', 0),
